3 Reading data
**************

The notebook case of study is to model DM in galaxies using PISO
density profile. The data analysed are rotation curve of spiral
galaxies.

   The format of the file must be:

   Rad	Vobs	 errV	 Vgas Vdisk Vbul SBdisk SBbul

   kpc	km/s	 km/s km/s  km/s  km/s L/pc^2 L/pc^2


